      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/1fafaaa8-1378-11e2-b63d-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
